import "./App.css";
import { BrowserRouter as Router, Switch, Route, Link } from "react-router-dom";
function App() {
  return (
    <>
      <Router>
        <Switch>
          <Route path="/home">
            <Home />
          </Route>
          <Route path="/about">
            <About />
          </Route>
          <Route path="/users">
            <Users />
          </Route>
          <Route path="/">
            <Home />
          </Route>
          <Route path="*">
            <ErrorPage />
          </Route>
        </Switch>
      </Router>
    </>
  );
}

export default App;
